m-recipe-instructions"><li id="wprm-recipe-22558-step-0-0" class="wprm-recipe-instruction" style="list-style-type: decimal;"><div class="wprm-recipe-instruction-text" style="margin-bottom: 5px;"><span style="display: block;">Prepare <a href="https://vegecravings.com/coriander-tomato-chutney-green-chutney">green chutney</a>. You can store this in the refrigerator for upto a week, or in the freezer for 2-3 weeks.</span></div><div class="wprm-recipe-instruction-media wprm-recipe-instruction-image" style="text-align: center;"><img data-lazyloaded="1" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4NjQiIGhlaWdodD0iNjQ4IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgODY0IDY0OCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgc3R5bGU9ImZpbGw6I2NmZDRkYjtmaWxsLW9wYWNpdHk6IDAuMTsiLz48L3N2Zz4=" decoding="async" width="864" height="648" data-src="https://vegecravings.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/coriander-tomato-chutney-recipe-step-by-step-instructions-1024x768.jpg" class="attachment-large size-large" alt="Coriander Tomato Chutney Recipe Step By Step Instructions" /></div></li><li id="wprm-recipe-22558-step-0-1" class="wprm-recipe-instruction" style="list-style-type: decimal;"><div class="wprm-recipe-instruction-text" style="margin-bottom: 5px;"><span style="display: block;">Prepare <a href="https://vegecravings.com/tamarind-chutney-recipe/">tamarind chutney (imli ki chutney)</a>. This chutney can be refrigerated for upto a month.</span></div><div class="wprm-recipe-instruction-media wprm-recipe-instruction-image" style="text-align: center;"><img data-lazyloaded="1" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4NjQiIGhlaWdodD0iNjg5IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgODY0IDY4OSI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgc3R5bGU9ImZpbGw6I2NmZDRkYjtmaWxsLW9wYWNpdHk6IDAuMTsiLz48L3N2Zz4=" decoding="async" width="864" height="689" data-src="https://vegecravings.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/tamarind-chutney-recipe-step-by-step-instructions-1024x816.jpg" class="attachment-large size-large" alt="Tamarind Chutney Recipe Step By Step Instructions" /></div></li><div class='code-block code-block-5' style='margin: 8px auto; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both;'>
