ight="671" data-src="https://vegecravings.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/batata-vada-recipe-step-by-step-instructions-4-1024x795.jpg" class="attachment-large size-large" alt="Batata Vada Recipe Step By Step Instructions 4" /></div></li><li id="wprm-recipe-22558-step-0-7" class="wprm-recipe-instruction" style="list-style-type: decimal;"><div class="wprm-recipe-instruction-text" style="margin-bottom: 5px;"><span style="display: block;">Take gram flour in a mixing bowl and add salt, red chilli powder &amp; turmeric powder to the mixture.</span></div><div class="wprm-recipe-instruction-ingredients wprm-recipe-instruction-ingredients-inline wprm-block-text-faded" style="margin-top: -5px; margin-bottom: 5px;"><span class="wprm-recipe-instruction-ingredient wprm-recipe-instruction-ingredient-22558-14" data-separator=", " style="margin-bottom: 5px;">1 Teaspoon Salt, </span><span class="wprm-recipe-instruction-ingredient wprm-recipe-instruction-ingredient-22558-15" data-separator=", " style="margin-bottom: 5px;">1/2 Teaspoon Red Chilli Powder, </span><span class="wprm-recipe-instruction-ingredient wprm-recipe-instruction-ingredient-22558-16" data-separator=", " style="margin-bottom: 5px;">1/2 Teaspoon Turmeric Powder (Haldi), </span><span class="wprm-recipe-instruction-ingredient wprm-recipe-instruction-ingredient-22558-13" data-separator="" style="margin-bottom: 5px;">1 Cup Besan (Gram Flour)</span></div><div class="wprm-recipe-instruction-media wprm-recipe-instruction-image" style="text-align: center;"><img data-lazyloaded="1" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4NjQiIGhlaWdodD0iNzMyIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgODY0IDczMiI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgc3R5bGU9ImZpbGw6I2NmZDRkYjtmaWxsLW9wYWNpdHk6IDAuMTsiLz48L3N2Zz4=" decoding="async" width="864" height="732" data-src="https://vegecravings.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/batata-vada-recipe-step-by-step-instructions-5-1024x868.jpg" class="attachment-large size-large" alt="Batata Vada Recipe Step By Step Instructions 5" /></div></li><div class='code-block code-block-7' style='margin: 8px auto; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both;'>
