ass="wprm-recipe-instruction" style="list-style-type: decimal;"><div class="wprm-recipe-instruction-text" style="margin-bottom: 5px;">Then fry the balls on medium-high flame till they turn golden brown.</div><div class="wprm-recipe-instruction-media wprm-recipe-instruction-image" style="text-align: center;"><img data-lazyloaded="1" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4NjQiIGhlaWdodD0iNzA3IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgODY0IDcwNyI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgc3R5bGU9ImZpbGw6I2NmZDRkYjtmaWxsLW9wYWNpdHk6IDAuMTsiLz48L3N2Zz4=" decoding="async" width="864" height="707" data-src="https://vegecravings.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/batata-vada-recipe-step-by-step-instructions-8-1024x838.jpg" class="attachment-large size-large" alt="Batata Vada Recipe Step By Step Instructions 8" /></div></li><div class='code-block code-block-8' style='margin: 8px 0; clear: both;'>
