December 30, 2018 at 12:07 am									</time>
</a></div></div></footer><div class="comment-content" itemprop="text"><p>Thank you for this yummy recipe. My wife and me wife are ardent lovers of authentic vada pav.  Here in Bengaluru we were missing those authentic Mumbai vada pav. I prepared it today &amp; my wife liked it very much. Once again thank you very much..</p>
